ADt/poem-IyRyJIpPDy12c4hKpMnwsA">Kinh sát hậu tiểu thuật - 京察後小述</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thang-Hi%E1%BB%83n-T%E1%BB%95/author-9UfZr60VQz5UUa1JmQS-sw">Thang Hiển Tổ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nam-S%E1%BB%AD/L%E1%BB%A5c-Th%E1%BA%AFng-tr%E1%BA%A1ch-thu-m%E1%BB%99-v%C5%A9-trung-th%C3%A1m-v%E1%BA%ADn-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-t%C3%A1c/poem-yz1mfrIBMLLGtQ8gGJhNvg">Lục Thắng trạch thu mộ vũ trung thám vận đồng tác - 陸勝宅秋暮雨中探韻同作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nam-S%E1%BB%AD/author-Wki6pPRclrS2pgLCHua9xQ">Trương Nam Sử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Nguy%C3%AAn-Tr%E1%BB%ABng/S%E1%BA%AFc-t%E1%BB%A9-T%C3%BA-Phong-t%E1%BB%B1-bi/poem-xxLxY7z4rcP4cV-gZh2gaw">Sắc tứ Tú Phong tự bi - 敕賜秀峰寺碑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Nguy%C3%AAn-Tr%E1%BB%ABng/author-_vSGbKXOej4AgRYmpqgykw">Hồ Nguyên Trừng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-036/poem-z7Q7L4meKdiyVX0bP3SzWg">Sơn cư bách vịnh kỳ 036 - 山居百詠其三十六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%C5%A9-phu-%C4%91%C3%B4i/poem-Qc80Uhzv026oTUhgUPuPxg">Vũ phu đôi - 珷玞堆</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
